    "rich_text_VJACiM": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_eHgLrY": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Updated 25 September 2025",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_8CemCT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>1. Summary</strong></p><p>The Mission Rewards Programme is a membership programme offered by Mission Estate Winery (<strong>Mission Estate Winery</strong>, <strong>we</strong>) to Mission Rewards Members (<strong>Member</strong>, <strong>you</strong>).</p><p>By applying for Mission Rewards Membership, you agree to these terms and conditions (<strong>Terms</strong>), which govern your membership to the Mission Rewards Programme.</p><p>Membership of the Mission Rewards Programme is not transferable with membership of any other programme or club.</p><p>We draw your attention to the following important provisions:</p><ul><li>We will collect and use your personal information in accordance with the Mission Estate Winery privacy statement and these Terms (paragraph 3)</li><li>You have certain obligations as a Mission Rewards Member (paragraph 2)</li><li>We may at our discretion change the Mission Rewards Member Benefits or Rewards from time to time (paragraph 8)</li><li>Mission Rewards Points, if not used, will expire one year after they were accrued to your Account, on the anniversary of the day they were earned (paragraph 11)</li><li>We limit our liability to you in respect of your Mission Rewards Membership (paragraph 17)</li></ul>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
        "text_dPBhkB": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>2. Your obligations</p><p>You must notify us promptly if you change your address or contact details.</p><p>You must keep your Membership number and your username and password details for your online Mission Rewards Membership Account secure.</p><p>You must login to your account, or present and quote your Mission Rewards number at the Cellar Door when make a Qualifying Purchase so that we can accrue Rewards Points to your Account.</p><p>You must not allow any other person to use your Mission Rewards number to earn Mission Rewards Points on your Account and you must not use any other person's Mission Rewards number to earn Mission Rewards Points on their Account, to do so would be engaging in fraud.</p><p>You must comply with the relevant terms and conditions applicable to any Mission Rewards Member Benefit you wish to redeem.</p><p>Mission Rewards Points are not convertible into cash.</p><p>You must not sell, assign or transfer Mission Rewards Points or any Mission Rewards Member Benefit to any other person for Cash or any other form of consideration.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
        "text_Pw4mB9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>3. Privacy Statement</p><p>By applying for Mission Rewards Membership to earn Mission Rewards Points, you authorise Mission Estate Winery to collect and use your personal information in accordance with our privacy statement as found on <a href=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\">www.missionestate.co.nz</a> and these Terms.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
