    "rich_text_AmGYQU": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_BifeGV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>4. Email communications</p><p>You acknowledge and agree that by providing us with your email address we may send you commercial electronic messages including but not limited to Mission Rewards Programme communications, Mission Rewards communications and Special Offers. </p><p>You may unsubscribe to our emails at any time by clicking on the 'unsubscribe link' in our emails. </p><p>It is your responsibility to keep your Account updated with your current email address.</p><p>5. Application for Mission Rewards Membership</p><p>Membership of the Mission Rewards Programme is personal to the Mission Rewards Member and is not transferable to any other person.</p><p>We reserve the right to accept or decline any application for Mission Rewards Membership. If your application is declined, we will inform you in writing.</p><p>Your Mission Rewards Membership will remain current until such time as it is terminated by either you or Mission Estate Winery pursuant to the termination provisions in paragraph 15.</p><p>6. Deceased Mission Rewards Member account closure</p><p>Following the date that we become aware of the death of a Mission Rewards Member, the deceased Member's Mission Rewards Account, Status Points, and all other Mission Rewards Member Benefits will be cancelled and become invalid. If we receive a written request by the executor of a Mission Rewards Member's estate to transfer the deceased Mission Rewards Member's current Mission Rewards Point balance to the Mission Rewards accounts of the beneficiaries of the Mission Rewards Member's estate, we will do so if we are satisfied that the request is valid and lawful and if the request is made within 2 years of the death of the Mission Rewards Member.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
        "text_hADx8p": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>7. <strong>Currency</strong></p><p>Credit is shown in New Zealand Dollars – as are all products and services within our online shop - for delivery in New Zealand.</p><p><strong>8. Mission Rewards Member benefits</strong></p><p>Mission Rewards Members can earn Mission Rewards Points to redeem Rewards and enjoy a range of Mission Rewards Member benefits.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
        "text_gPQL6x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>9. Earning Mission Rewards Points</p><p>Mission Rewards Members may earn Mission Rewards Points on Qualifying Purchases or through other methods as outlined on our Mission Rewards Page of our website, <a href=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\">www.missionestate.co.nz</a>.</p><p>To earn Mission Rewards Points, you must quote your Mission Rewards Account number at the time of making a making a Qualifying Purchase at our Cellar Door or be logged into your account online before making the Qualifying Purchase.  </p><p>Points cannot be added to your account after the purchase has been made. </p><p>10. Qualifying purchases</p><p>You may earn Mission Rewards points by making Qualifying Purchases with Mission Estate Cellar Door or from our online shop at <a href=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\">www.missionestate.co.nz</a>.  The Mission Rewards may be earned on the value of the purchase excluding shipping costs and GST.</p><p>We may at our discretion vary the range and type of Qualifying Purchases.  Purchases of Restaurant Vouchers, Farmhouse Accommodation, Concert or purchases made at Mission Restaurant do not qualify for Mission Rewards Points.</p><p>11. Mission Rewards Points expiry</p><p>Your Mission Rewards Points will remain valid for one year from the date they were accrued to your Account. Following one year from accrual, the Mission Rewards Points will expire and be removed from your Account on the anniversary of the day they were earned.</p><p>We endeavour to notify you by email prior to expiration of any Mission Rewards Points, however we hold no responsibility if, for whatever reason this email notification does not get sent, or, if it is not received by the Member for any reason.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
