    "rich_text_mqGQcE": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_jzhKda": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>12. Spending Mission Rewards Credit</strong></p><p>You may use your Mission Rewards Points to make purchases at our Cellar Door in person or via our online shop at <a href=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.missionestate.co.nz\">www.missionestate.co.nz</a> .</p><p>At our discretion we may change what is available for purchase using Mission Rewards Points.</p><p>The following requirements apply to all Rewards:</p><ul><li>We do not guarantee that any of the Rewards will be available at any time and we reserve the right to withdraw, cancel, change or suspend any of the Rewards we offer or advertise. We are not liable for any loss, expense, or damage any Member suffers as a result of such withdrawal, cancellation, suspension or change.</li></ul><p>13. Notice and contact details</p><p>Any notice given by us to you pursuant to these Terms and will be deemed to have been given and received by you if we email the notice to you at the email address shown on your Membership Account.</p><p>As our primary means of contact with you, it is your responsibility to always maintain an up-to-date email address on your account.  Mission Estate Winery will not be held accountable for notifications going to out of date or expired email addresses.</p><p>14. Changes to these Terms</p><p>We may make changes to these Terms from time to time. When we make changes, we will update these Terms on our website. We will also specify the date of the last update.</p><p>The changes we may make to these Terms include but are not limited to changing: the requirements relating to the Mission Rewards Member Benefits; the Mission Rewards Points earning rates; the redemption rates for Rewards and the qualifying purchases. For example, we may vary the products or services which can be used to earn Mission Rewards Points.</p><p><strong>15. Termination</strong></p><p>You may terminate your Mission Rewards Membership at any time online.</p><p>If a Mission Rewards Membership is terminated by either the Mission Rewards Member or by us (other than due to death of the Mission Rewards Member), any Mission Rewards Credit the Mission Rewards Member has earned but not redeemed prior to termination will be forfeited with no compensation.</p><p>Mission Rewards Membership will automatically terminate on the death or bankruptcy of a Mission Rewards Member.</p><p>Your Mission Rewards Account may not have a negative Mission Rewards Points balance but if it does, it may be closed without notice. </p><p>Mission Estate Winery may terminate or suspend your Mission Rewards Membership or cancel or suspend your right to access to Mission Rewards Membership Benefits by notice in writing if we reasonably believe that you have:</p><ul><li>Abused, misused or obtained by any misrepresentation any Mission Rewards Points, Mission Rewards Member Benefits or other facilities or arrangements provided by or in connection with the Mission Rewards Programme;</li><li>Behaved in a manner which Mission Estate Winery reasonably considers to be unacceptable while using any Mission Rewards Member Benefits or other facilities, services, or arrangements provided by or in connection with the Mission Rewards Programme;</li><li>Acted in any way that is detrimental to the interests of Mission Estate Winery or the Mission Rewards Programme; or</li><li>Provided incorrect or misleading information to Mission Estate Winery in connection with your Mission Rewards Membership.</li></ul><p>If we decide to discontinue the Mission Rewards Programme we may terminate your Mission Rewards Membership by giving you 1 month written notice.</p><p>If we cease to operate, we may terminate Mission Rewards Membership any time without notice.</p><p><strong>16. Limitation of liability</strong></p><p>Subject to applicable consumer protection laws and to the fullest extent permitted by law, you agree that Mission Estate Winery will have no liability (in negligence, tort, breach of contract, or otherwise) for any loss or damage (including direct or indirect loss, or special or consequential loss or damage) arising out of or in connection with:</p><ul><li>Our variation to these Terms from time to time;</li><li>Our variation of Mission Rewards Member Benefits from time to time;</li><li>Your participation in a Mission Rewards Account </li><li>Our termination of your Mission Rewards Membership in accordance with these Terms;</li><li>The use of (or inability to use), the availability of, and or the lack of suitability of any Mission Rewards Member Benefit for you or anyone else;</li><li>The Mission Rewards  Points that you forfeit upon termination of your Mission Rewards Membership;</li><li>The availability of Rewards, Mission Rewards Member Benefits, </li><li>Our failure or delay to provide Rewards due to force majeure, pandemic, or other events beyond our control;</li><li>Your legal and tax obligations and liabilities;</li><li>Any unauthorised or fraudulent activity in relation to your Mission Rewards Membership and Account in circumstances where the person attempting or carrying out the activity:</li><li>Represents themselves to Mission Estate Winery as you and provides Mission Estate Winery with your Mission Rewards Membership number; or</li><li>Uses your online Mission Estate Winery Account username and password.</li><li>The breach in the security of your computer, mobile or other device or the access to any information held on your computer, mobile or other device by unauthorised third parties. You are responsible for ensuring the security of the personal information held on your computer, mobile or other device.</li></ul><p>Nothing in these Terms shall exclude or limit our liability for death or personal injury caused by negligence or for fraud and fraudulent misrepresentation.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        },
        "text_4J4zmH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>17. Disclaimers</strong></p><p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Mission Estate Winery makes no warranties (express or implied), and makes no representations with respect to:</p><ul><li>To the suitability of the Mission Rewards Programme or Mission Rewards Member Benefits for you or anyone else;</li><li>The ability (or inability) to redeem any Reward by you or anyone else;</li><li>Your compliance with laws in the country in which you reside, including any laws that may relate to you earning and redeeming Mission Rewards Points. You are responsible for ensuring your compliance with all relevant local laws in the country of your residence.</li><li>You are responsible for ensuring you comply with the legal age required to purchase alcohol in your country of residence.</li></ul><p>18. Laws of New Zealand apply</p><p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of New Zealand. You and Mission Estate Winery consent to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of New Zealand in connection with any legal action that may arise in relation to these Terms, your Mission Rewards Membership and/or the Mission Rewards Programme.</p><p>If you reside in New Zealand you must be above the age of 18 to join Mission Rewards Programme as this is the legal age required to purchase alcohol in New Zealand.</p><p>19. Miscellaneous</p><p>If any term or provision of these Terms is held to be illegal, invalid or unenforceable it will be severed from the Terms without affecting the legality, validity or enforceability of the remaining provisions.</p><p>Additional information about the Mission Rewards Programme may be found on the Mission Estate Winery website. To the extent of any inconsistency, these Terms, as amended from time to time, shall prevail.</p><p>We reserve the right to audit each Mission Rewards Account. We reserve the right to amend, debit and correct the Mission Rewards Credit and/or Status Point balance in a Mission Rewards Account if we identify any inaccuracy (due to our mistake or otherwise), or if we identify that the Qualifying Purchase was not paid for in full.</p><p>We reserve the right to audit your Account and Mission Rewards Membership.</p><p>We reserve the right to adjust the Mission Rewards Credit and Status Points balance in your Account if we identify any inaccuracy.</p><p><strong>20. Definitions</strong></p><p>In these Terms:</p><p>The terms used in these Terms and Conditions have the following meanings:</p><p><strong>Account or Mission Rewards Account</strong> means the record maintained online that you may access as a registered user of our website with your Mission Rewards login and password to view your Mission Rewards balance details.</p><p><strong>The records</strong> include the Member Details, Mission Rewards credit earned through Qualifying Purchases, the Mission Rewards credit deducted following the redemption of your Mission Rewards credit for Qualifying Purchases, the Status Points earned and current Tier Status.</p><p><strong>Mission Rewards Programme</strong> means the customer loyalty programme for Mission Rewards Members operated by Mission Estate Winery in accordance with these Terms.</p><p><strong>Mission Estate Winery</strong>, <strong>MEW</strong>, <strong>we, our</strong> and <strong>us</strong> means Mission Estate Winery, which is the trading name for Marist Holdings (Greenmeadows) Ltd.</p>",
            "font_desk": 18,
            "font_mob": 16
          }
        }
      },
